<br>
AC?  AC is not the end-all of PvP.  It can be very important in a melee joust, but it isn't *that* important.  Sv Magic / Poison / Disease / Fire / Cold are insanely important in a PvP battle, and I personally prefer my fights to be based on equipment and skill more than level.  If you prefer to see red cons decimate you because they sat on a kobold longer, good for you; we simply disagree.<br>
