Resistance equipment is far easier to camp than levels are.<br>
<br>
If you can get level 35, you can get 100+ MR.<br>
<br>
Therefore, it works out.  Equipment requires some thought (planning, selecting necessary pieces) to boost your resistances in the correct manner, and is attainable by a fairly &quot;low&quot; level (35).  Levels are simply killing the same AI-based mob over and over again with the same old stale tactics you used on level 5 mobs.  Skill is, well, skill.<br>
<br>
Given a choice, I'd rather the first and last be deciding my PvP encounters than the center.<br>
