<br>
This would mean that resist gear and levels would be of somewhat equal importance as resists make you harder to kill but levels make it easier to kill others.  If resists worked this way it would be entirely possible for someone who took time away from leveling to build up the right equipment to take down someone who powerleveled up past them by xping constantly and not bothering to pay attention to equipment.  Obviously one would be more offensive and the other more defensive and the higher level char would still have some advantage due to unresistable spells and such but at least it wouldn't be impossible for the lower level with higher resists to fight back. <p>--------------------<BR>
